title: Wilhemina Venable Scenes || Apocalypse

comment: Ms. Venable is one of my favorite AHS villains, especially since she's played by the wonderful Sarah Paulson.  Venable is the type of villain who isn't evil; just broken.  Wish I could put her back together.  I adore Sarah Paulson and every character she plays. 💞💞💞
